# Sentinel file. The top-level Makefile sources Makefile.platform via:
#     -include Makefile.platform
# The leading dash is intentional: even on a checkout that somehow
# lacks the include file, `make` will not abort; the platform targets
# simply will not be available. This file exists so the ordering
# contract is explicit and discoverable from `git log` if anyone
# wonders why the include is there.
